@0    = ~Move out of way!  ~
@1    = ~Whoa... hold on a second.  I have a few questions for you.~
@2    = ~How rude.  I think it's time someone taught you some manners.~
@3    = ~Whatever you say, big fella.  The road is yours.  Farewell.~
@4    = ~Red Toe has no time to speak with puny peoples.  Must run away.~
@5    = ~Red Toe?  Who is Red Toe?~
@6    = ~What kind of name is Red Toe?~
@7    = ~Run away from what?~
@8    = ~As you wish.  Farewell.~
@9    = ~Red Toe no need *man-nurz.*  Only needs to run away.  Now move out of way or Red Toe squish you all.~
@10   = ~You're not too bright, are you?~
@11   = ~Sorry, but the world will be a much better place without you in it.  Hold still... this will only hurt for a moment.~
@12   = ~Me Red Toe.  Great verbeeg warrior.~
@13   = ~If you're such a great warrior, why are you fleeing this place in such a hurry?~
@14   = ~It's a pleasure to meet you Red Toe.  Now, it's going to be an even greater pleasure to kill you.~
@15   = ~When Red Toe was child, he drops big rock on foot.  Rock smashes foot and makes him yell.  Other verbeeg laugh and call him Red Toe.  ~
@16   = ~I see.  Why are you in such a hurry?  What are you running from?~
@17   = ~Red Toe running from holy place.  He runs so he no die like others.~
@18   = ~Holy Place?  You mean the temple over yonder?~
@19   = ~What others?  What are you talking about?~
@20   = ~Yes.  Red Toe was guard for friend priests in holy place.  But then bad priests come.  Begin killing friend priests and other verbeeg guards with hurtful magic.  But Red Toe smart.  He falls on ground and makes bad priests think he's dead.  When they gone, Red Toe gets up and runs from holy place.~
@21   = ~Tell me about these "bad priests."  Why did they attack the temple?~
@22   = ~You're nothing but a cowardly deserter... you don't deserve to live.  Die!~
@23   = ~Pretty smart... for a big barbarian ass.  Off you go then, but don't let me catch you anywhere near Kuldahar.~
@24   = ~Others.  Inside holy place.  Red Toe not go back there.  Not safe for verbeeg anymore.~
@25   = ~No place is safe for cowardly deserters while we're around. Time for you to die, brute!~
@26   = ~Very well.  Off you go then, but don't let me catch you anywhere near Kuldahar.~
@27   = ~Red Toe very smart!  That why he not dead like others inside holy place.  That why he runs now.~
@28   = ~No!  Red Toe done talking!  Now he runs.  Runs away before bad priests come back and kill him too!~
